    <h1><strong><font size="5">How to stay safe from bad weather conditions:</font></strong></h1>

    <p><font size="4">1. Avoid contact with conductors of electricity, appliances, metal objects and water.</font></p>
    <p><font size="4">2.Take safe shelter immediately inside a sturdy building, away from windows, doors and electrical appliances.</font></p>
    <p><font size="4">3.Wear several layers of loose fitting, lightweight, warm clothing rather than one layer of heavy clothing. The outer garments should be tightly woven and water repellent.</font></p>
    <p><font size="4">4.Wear a hat. Cover your mouth with a scarf to protect your lungs. </font></p>


------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
