    <p><font size="4">1.Try to stay out of the sun, particularly when it is at its highest between 11am and 3pm.</font></p>
    <p><font size="4">2.Stock up on supplies like medicines, food and non-alcoholic drinks, so you won’t have to go out in the heat.</font></p>
